<p>The temperature deduction value (H) is the larger of two point deduction values; (h1) or (h2).  
(h1) is calculated from an equation that uses EGDD.  (h2) is calculated from an equation that
uses (GSL).</p>

<p>The Temperature Factor is then caluculated as 100 - (H).</p>



